{"synckey":1604837567,"updated":[{"bookId":"24953102","bookmarkId":"24953102_18_501-873","chapterUid":18,"markText":"只要在这样的意识下进行思考并实际尝试写文章，任何人都能写出一定水准之上的东西。构建文章时的流程，基本上分为以下三个步骤：①找到想写的主题（或是发现、主张）②由主题创造三个关键概念，即“想说的事”③将三个关键概念联结起来，构建文章要想掌握这一流程，写小论文、企划方案或评论等需要有逻辑且客观的文章，是非常有效的方法。","range":"501-873","createTime":1604837567,"type":1},{"bookId":"24953102","bookmarkId":"24953102_7_1406-1459","chapterUid":7,"markText":"以“因为○○是△△（逗号）所以能得出××的结论（句号）”的形式，像写文章一样录入对话，然后再边听边写出来。","range":"1406-1459","createTime":1604828682,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"将文章比作建筑物","chapterUid":18,"chapterIdx":18},{"title":"当代商务人士需要具备的“说写两用力”","chapterUid":7,"chapterIdx":7}],"book":{"bookId":"24953102","version":1052826575,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/26/YueWen_24953102/s_YueWen_24953102.jpg","title":"职场实用写作课（套装共4册）","author":"斋藤孝 劳拉·布朗等","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KTR2btN4tD$vflkFg9t2Rg","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#351200"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3b0c00"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#420300"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#482913"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#502500"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#562100"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#624027"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#6a3d14"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#703900"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#7a3300"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#86552a"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#924f00"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#7d583c"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#b1680c"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#977255"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#ab6b2b"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b18c6e"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#bd885a"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#c78544"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#d57f00"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#e39f5e"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#ec9c46"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#f49927"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#e7c19f"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#f4bd8b"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ffb342"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f4e0cd"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffce5d"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#c78544"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#e39f5e"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3EDE5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3EDE5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#271300"}],"domin